<HEADLINE> World Women Entrepreneurs Trade Fair to Open in </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, October 14 (Xinhua) -- The Organization of
African Unity (OAU) announced Wednesday that the Second Global
Women Entrepreneurs Trade Fair will be held here from October 15
to 23.
</P>
<P>
An OAU press release issued here said the government and the
people of Ethiopia are assisting with the preparations of
the investment forum which is scheduled to be held from October
20 to 23 in Addis Ababa.
</P>
