<HEADLINE> Ethiopian FM Visits Egypt </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, October 14 (Xinhua) -- Ethiopian Foreign Minister
Seyoum Mesfin Wednesday left here for Cairo to pay a two-day
working visit to Egypt, reported the Ethiopian News Agency.
</P>
<P>
Seyoum will convey a message from Ethiopian Prime Minister
Meles Zenawi to President Hosni Mubarak of Egypt.
</P>
<P>
