companies nationwide, ended with a total trade volume of over 1.2
billion yuan (145 million US dollars).
</P>
<P>
The 17th fair was largest of its kind held in China over the
past five years in terms of number of participants, new products
and trade volume.
</P>
<P>
China has scored remarkable achievements in restructuring and
realigning its motorcycle industry, with sales rebounding and
competition becoming increasingly fierce.  
