<HEADLINE> Li Peng on Regional Environmental Protection Cooperation (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUILIN, October 15 (Xinhua) -- Li Peng, the chairman of the
Standing Committee of the National People's Congress, spoke today
about the Asia-Pacific region's environmental protection and
sustainable development.
</P>
<P>
Parliaments, governments and non-governmental organizations of
those countries in the region have common interests and similar
long-range goals and can do a lot in this area, he told the 6th
General Assembly of the Asia-Pacific Parliamentarians Conference
on the Environment and Development that opened here today.
</P>
