environmental and development matters and has made an effort to
increase international and regional cooperation. In recent years,
the National People's Congress has developed laws and regulations
on environmental protection and formed the legal framework for
controlling environmental pollution and for law enforcement, he
said.
</P>
<P>
In March 1997, the National People's Congress decided that any
act leading to serious environmental damage is a crime. By the end
of last year, China closed 65,000 small factories that were
causing pollution and formulated a national plan for improving the
environment.
</P>
<P>
China has made its contributions to the international
environmental and developmental cause, he said.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19981015.0135 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-15 </DATE_TIME>
