<HEADLINE> Results of Denish Open Badminton (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, October 15 (Xinhua) -- Following are the first
round results from the Danish Open badminton championships on
Thursday:
</P>
<P>
