Ogi, the first Swiss defense minister to visit China since the
two countries established diplomatic ties 48 years ago, discussed
army reforms in Switzerland.
</P>
<P>
Lieutenant General Xiong Guangkai, deputy chief of general
staff of the PLA, was present at the talk. 
