<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, October 15 (Xinhua) -- A series of landslides triggered
by strong winds and heavy rains unleashed by Supertyphoon Zeb
killed six people in the northern city of Baguio, it was learned
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
