<HEADLINE> Colombia Sees Foreign Direct Investment Up 212 Percent </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTAFE DE BOGOTA, October 14 (Xinhua) -- Colombia saw its
foreign direct investment (FDI) climb to 3.325 billion
U.S. dollars during the first six months of this year, up 212
percent over the same period last year.
</P>
<P>
